<p class="MsoNoSpacing"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;">Where:&nbsp;</span></span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: 12px;">in the Ocean of Peace Meditation Hall, Deer Park Monastery</span></p>
