<p><em>The basic meditation sutras,</em></p>
<p><em>such as the Full Awareness of Breathing and the Four Establishments of Mindfulness,</em></p>
<p><em>show us step by step,</em></p>
<p><em>how to transform the body and the mind.</em></p>
