<p><em><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;">Emptiness, signlessness, and aimlessness</span></em><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;"></span></p>
<p><em><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;">liberate me from suffering,</span></em><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: black;"></span></p>
